## 🏢 Organizer Role: Creating an Event
**Objective:** Log in as an organizer and create a new event.

![Organizer Event Created](file:///C:/Users/Palgun%20Bharadwaj%20S/.gemini/antigravity/brain/785142c2-d336-4859-8f8f-dc0b52fc062f/organizer_event_created_1777544970180.png)

