## 🛠️ Admin Role: Approval & Deletion
**Objective:** Log in as an admin to approve pending events and delete/reject events.

````carousel
![Admin Event Approved](file:///C:/Users/Palgun%20Bharadwaj%20S/.gemini/antigravity/brain/785142c2-d336-4859-8f8f-dc0b52fc062f/admin_event_approved_1777545031587.png)
